      <t>&lt;p&gt;Counter with CBC-MAC (CCM) is a generic authenticated encryption block cipher mode.  CCM is defined for use with 128-bit block ciphers, such as the Advanced Encryption Standard (AES).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
